    Yuzhny (Russia, Kaliningrad Oblast), 4 April 2013.


    LETTER OF THANKS


    To the President and residents of the city of Gdańsk,

    Mr. Krzysztof Frączak,

    The “Spiritual Dimension of Europe” Foundation


    We sincerely thank you for the humanitarian aid in the form of computer
    equipment for the students of our school. Thanks to your help, the children
    will be able to gain new knowledge through the Internet and communicate with
    peers from abroad.


    School Principal

    N. A. Viedzishchev


    Yuzhnoye village,

    April 2013
